      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "it's definitely pretty painful but i'm pretty sure it's just a bad sprain. i've seen people do this all the time and just walk it off after a few days of rest. if i just take a bunch of ibuprofen to knockdown the swelling and keep it elevated, i'll be good to go by the weekend right? i really just want to avoid the clinic if i can help it.",
